
Click on "Consultation and Registration Fee(s)"


        > Select the patients name

        > Click on "Receive Payment" (at bottom left side.)



        > Enter the AMOUNT RECEIVED  
                (Note that you cannot enter anything less that the bill amount)

        > Click Save
        
        
        Similarly, you can take payment for all the individual bills
        - Lab Bills
        - Procedure Bills
        - Pharmacy Bills
        - Nurses Billing Sheet
        - GRAND TOTAL BILL  
                This is for paying everything altogether at once 
                however, it will not show the details of the payment on the reciept
                
        - Itemized Bill - This can be printed out for a patient who wants to see all their payment details
